Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,白天出发肯定会更安全\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Surely it would have been safer to do this during daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.09,0:01:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们本来就应该在白天转移\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We would have been expected to do this during daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,‎虽然我们称他们为"黑暗生物"\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We may call them night creatures,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.71,0:01:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但他们在阳光下行动自如\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}but they operate perfectly when in sunshine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.76,0:01:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但可以肯定 ‎指挥他们的吸血鬼受不了白天\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But surely the vampires who command them are disadvantaged by daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.92,0:01:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们的黑暗生物显然听从命令\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Their night creatures are clearly being instructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.96,0:01:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这些攻击目标很明确\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The attacks are too targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.51,0:01:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,‎所以我们要在他们接到新命令前转移\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So we're moving before they can be given fresh orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.71,0:01:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 希望这样能活下来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We live in hope, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.92,0:01:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们有机会赶在被他们发现\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And our chances of making it to your castle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.88,0:01:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,‎下达新命令之前到达你的城堡吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}before we're spotted and those fresh orders are given?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.26,0:01:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我想 几乎没什么机会\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, somewhere between slim and none, I would imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,‎要是我想听你说话 ‎我会往你的乞讨碗里扔钱的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}When I want to hear from you, I'll throw a coin in your begging bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.38,0:01:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,‎所有这一切 还有魔法流浪汉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}All this and a magical tramp.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.38,0:01:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,‎"魔法"\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}"Magical"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我一辈子都住在这里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I've lived out here my whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.21,0:02:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们住在森林和溪流的精灵旁边\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We live next to the spirits of wood and stream,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.17,0:02:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,它们伴随着暴风雨和魔法的气息而来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}the things that come with the storm and the smell of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.00,0:02:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你能闻出来 ‎他散发着这种气息\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You smell of it. He reeks of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.88,0:02:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你觉得闻起来是什么气息\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What does it smell like to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.26,0:02:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你的气息像香料一样甜\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}On you, it's sweet like spices.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.92,0:02:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他身上是腐烂的味道\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}On him, it's rotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.17,0:02:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是啊 我的耳朵都快腐烂聋了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes, it's... it's rendered me quite deaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.63,0:02:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我只是个学者 夫人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I am but a scholar, madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.30,0:02:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你闻到的气息要归功于‎阿鲁卡多最近用的香皂\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The scents you detect are entirely down to Alucard having recently used soap
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.44,0:02:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,‎而我要和你的鸡争着用池塘里的水\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and my having to fight your chickens for access to pond water.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,‎还争输了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,‎确实输了 我是个学者\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And indeed losing. I am a man of books.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.02,0:02:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我很不喜欢你那土里土气的农民做派\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Your earthy peasant ways are quite beyond me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.48,0:02:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我有其他方面的专长\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}My skills lie in other directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.48,0:02:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎真遗憾 ‎我希望你擅长用刀\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Pity. I was hoping you were good with a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.15,0:02:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我要巡视一圈 确保没有人掉队\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm going to circle around and make sure I don't have stragglers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,‎只是个学者吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Just a scholar, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:02:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,‎还很擅长发明饮料\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, and very good at inventing drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.69,0:03:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我以前认识的一个人会喜欢你这一点\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I used to know someone who would have liked that about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我以前认识的一个人喜欢我这一点\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I used to know someone who liked that about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我希望很快能再见到她\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I hope to see her again soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我希望你如愿 ‎你的话听起来令人欣慰\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I hope you do. That sounds comforting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 是的 ‎谢谢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,‎继续走\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Keep walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,‎没错\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不准你们求救\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No calls for help from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这看起来是不是太辛苦了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Doesn't it look absolutely bloody exhausting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.37,0:04:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,‎快走 老兄\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Move, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你没想过把箭从他脑袋里取出来吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Could you seriously not have considered taking the arrow out of his brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,‎拔出来就行了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Just pull the thing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不能直接拔箭\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You can't just pull arrows out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,‎如果把箭拽出来 ‎箭头后面的倒钩\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The barbs on the back of the arrowhead tear the flesh open
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.33,0:05:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,会把肉撕裂\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}if you yank the thing free.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.71,0:05:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你知道他已经死了吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You do know he's already dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.83,0:05:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你想醒来时眼窝里插着箭吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Would you want to wake up with an arrowhead filling your eye socket?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,‎好了 现在...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}There.  Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,‎带下一个过来前 ‎试着先动动脑子 好吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}let's try thinking for a moment before bringing the next one in, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你重返人间了 喘口气\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You're back in the world. Take a breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这里现在是你的家\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This is your place now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这两个人会给你做标记 ‎把你送到你要去的地方\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}These two will mark you out and take you where you need to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,‎下一个\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我能不能说...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Can I just say...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我觉得这个渎神的过程令人恶心\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}that I find this whole blasphemous process disgusting?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那你为什么还坐在那里看\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Then why are you sitting there watching it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,‎因为我想好好表达厌恶\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Because I want to hate it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你没有别的事要做吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Don't you have anything better to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,0:06:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不 在外面等我叫你们\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No. Wait outside until I call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,‎有什么事 丽诺尔\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What's wrong, Lenore?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.04,0:06:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,‎没什么 你觉得能有什么事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Nothing's wrong. What makes you say something's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:06:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我有眼睛和耳朵 ‎我知道有些事不对劲\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I've got eyes and ears. I know when something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,‎好吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,‎如果卡米拉独自离开太久\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}When Carmilla's left on her own for too long,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.31,0:07:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,‎她就开始谋划\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}she starts to scheme,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.81,0:07:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这对我们来说真的很好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and that works out really well for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.31,0:07:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,施第里尔可能是世界上最古老的吸血鬼的稳定领地\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Styria might be the oldest stable vampire community in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‎当然也是女性执掌的唯一领地\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}certainly the only one run by women.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我太高兴了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm overjoyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.23,0:07:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,‎闭嘴\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Shush.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,‎莫拉娜和斯崔格走了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Morana and Striga are away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我忙着接手莫拉娜的部分工作\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I've been busy taking care of some of Morana's work
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‎花时间和你待在一起\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and spending time with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.94,0:07:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,‎卡米拉总是独自行事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and Carmilla's been on her own a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.77,0:07:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‎现在 你知道施第里尔是怎么维持这么长时间的吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Now, do you know how Styria has lasted so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,‎因为你们是聪明伶俐的吸血鬼姐妹吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Because you're all very clever vampire sisters?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.65,0:07:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你还真是观察入微\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You've been paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.11,0:07:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是的 但也是因为我们没有过度扩张\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes, but also because we didn't overreach.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,‎吸血鬼天性饥渴 丽诺尔\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Vampires are thirsty, Lenore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这是你们的本性\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's what defines you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,‎在附近的田野里总是有地方可以吸血\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}There's always more blood to be drunk somewhere across the next field.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.48,0:07:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但我们没有那样做 真的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But we didn't do that, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:07:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但现在我…\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But now I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.36,0:08:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不知道...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I don't know, and it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这让我感到有点迷失了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's leaving me feeling a bit lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,‎好像我在我们体系里的地位被抹杀了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Like my place in our system has been erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.91,0:08:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我觉得你是我要解决的最后的难题\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I think you were the last problem I had to solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.66,0:08:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是的 再次谢谢你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes. Thanks again for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,‎闭嘴 你玩得挺开心\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, shush. You were having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,‎嗯 直接说正题吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, right up until almost the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但你要说的是另一件事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But you're making another point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,‎难怪我这么喜欢你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This is why I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你可以认真听我说\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You're capable of actually listening to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,‎也许等到我老死了 ‎你才能说完另一件事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Maybe you'll reach your other point before I die of old age.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们四个人相互扶持\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The four of us support each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.58,0:08:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但很快我就没事可做了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But soon I'll have nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,‎没有用处了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Nothing to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不用外交手段 ‎也能让人类排队等着被吸血\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}There's no diplomacy involved in making humans stand in line to be bled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,‎所有的人类\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}All the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,‎-而且不只是在欧洲  ‎-是吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}- And not just in Europe. - Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.66,0:08:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,‎她给我看了她的地图\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}She showed me her maps.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.87,0:08:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我想 我惹她生气了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I made her angry, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,‎她给我看了世界地图\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}She showed me maps of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.75,0:08:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我知道 我知道\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:09:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,‎从这里到布勒伊拉 ‎巨大的人类畜栏 我听说了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}A giant human pen from here to Braila. I've had the lectures.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不仅如此\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.09,0:09:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,‎她一直在谋划\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}She's been scheming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,‎她给我看了世界地图 赫克托\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And she showed me maps of the world, Hector.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.62,0:09:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,‎世界\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这个畜栏是为了确保我们 ‎以后几百年的生存和保障\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The pen was about securing our survival and safety for centuries to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这是个疯狂的想法 ‎但我们能延续和实施这个计划\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It was an insane idea, but we could stretch and make it work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但现在 她看到了无处不在的弱点\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But now she sees weakness everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们曾经是强大而稳定的领地\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And we were a strong and stable community
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.91,0:09:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,‎在这个世界上 ‎许多吸血鬼领袖死在布勒伊拉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}in a world that lost many of its vampire leaders at Braila.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.12,0:09:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,‎所以你是说 如果真是这样的情况 她会去征服世界\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So what you're saying is if it's there, she's going to drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,‎她说她有个计划\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}She said she had one plan:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,‎吞并从这里到海洋的土地\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}To annex land from here to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.50,0:09:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,‎她向我保证 那是她的计划\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}She promised me that was her plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,‎然后她就独自离去\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and then she was left alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,‎后来我惹她生气 她就给我看了地图\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and then I made her angry and she showed me her maps.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:09:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我觉得她骗了你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I think she lied to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,‎就像德古拉骗了我一样\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Just the way Dracula lied to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.75,0:10:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,‎看 他们死了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Look at them die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.62,0:10:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我知道你们都又累又怕\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I know you're all tired and scared,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.21,0:10:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但他们只是该死的畜生\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}but they're just bloody animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,‎杀了那些杂种\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Kill the bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我的家人几代前来到这里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}My family came here generations ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,‎据说他们逃离了罗马人的魔爪\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They escaped from the Romans, so the story goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.37,0:10:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你的家族可能起源于迦太基 ‎也许是更远的地方\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You could probably trace your family back to Carthage, perhaps further.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我的家族就在这里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}My family's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,‎从德内什蒂建成和命名以来 ‎我们一直住在这里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We've been in Danesti since it was just a wide spot in the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,‎人们从四面八方来到这里定居\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}People from all over wash up here and stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们的起源地不是别处\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We don't trace back to anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们都来自这里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We're all from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,‎起源于某个地方\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That must be nice,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:10:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,‎一定很不错\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to be from somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,‎好吧...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.48,0:11:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们已经不在那里了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}we're not there anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.94,0:11:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,‎说来惭愧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And then, I'm ashamed to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.11,0:11:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我像父亲一样 ‎把他们挂在城堡外的木桩上\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I put them on stakes outside the castle like I was my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,‎好吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我只想说\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm just saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:11:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我的状态不太好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I am not at my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,‎确实很…\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It has been...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,‎艰难\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我看得出来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.02,0:12:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我曾经同时有男朋友和女朋友\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I mean, I had a boyfriend and a girlfriend at the same time once,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但他们没打算杀我\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}but they never tried to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.90,0:12:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,‎其实 不是这样的 我说谎了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Actually, no. I tell a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.45,0:12:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他妻子拿着干草叉来打我\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}His wife went for me with a pitchfork.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我知道你很古怪\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I knew you'd be strange,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但我没想到 ‎这种事情会让你回归生活\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}but I didn't think it would be something like this that brought you back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,‎一直有这样的事情\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's always something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,‎战争吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}A war?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,‎总是看起来像战争\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It always looks like a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但其实是拯救\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But really, it's a rescue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.83,0:12:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,‎独处 然后战斗 拯救\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Alone. Then the fight. The rescue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.54,0:12:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,‎然后再独处\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Then alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我也许应该完全长大了 ‎现在就接受现实\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I should probably grow all the way up and accept it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,‎还有更糟的事情\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}There are worse things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你可能屁股上插着棍子 被‎挂在别人的城堡外面\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You could be outside someone else's castle with a stake up your bum.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.23,0:13:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们似乎掌握诀窍了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They seem to be getting the hang of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,‎像你说的 他们累了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}As you said, they were tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这种日子过得太久了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They've been living through this too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不想被打扰是很正常的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's only natural to want to sleep through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.87,0:13:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,‎听起来像是你的经验\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That sounded like you spoke from experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.25,0:13:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,‎好像是很久以前的事了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It seems like a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.46,0:13:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,‎德拉甘 你这该死的笨蛋\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Dragan, you bloody fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.96,0:13:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,‎要是你演的这出好戏把我们都害死了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}If this little show you're putting on gets us all killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那就白干了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}this was for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.96,0:13:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不会后退的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm not backing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:13:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,‎给我点空间就行\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Just give me some space.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我是来应战的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I came to do a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我请求你允许我来出手\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm asking your permission to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.75,0:14:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,‎好的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.48,0:15:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,‎德古拉的城堡\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Dracula's castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.23,0:15:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,‎令人惊叹\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Astonishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,‎真的很…\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's really quite...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,‎难看死了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Ugly as sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不难看\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's not ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.47,0:16:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,‎很难看\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,很悲伤\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And it's sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,‎还很冷\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这里会有倒霉事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Bad things happened here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.69,0:16:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你说的可是我童年的家\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That's my childhood home you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,‎难怪你这么奇怪\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, that explains a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.15,0:16:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,‎对不起\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,‎有些地方让人不寒而栗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Some places just have a chill on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,‎也许我和我的人能让这里暖和一点\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Maybe my people and I can warm it up a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.52,0:16:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,‎太宏伟了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我相信是贝尔蒙特庄园\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The Belmont Hold, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我亲爱的女士\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This, my dear lady,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.94,0:16:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这可能是现代世界最重要的地方\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}may be the most important place in the modern world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.65,0:16:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,‎目前 这是我能想到最好的防守要地\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}At this moment, it is the best defense I can think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,‎欢迎来到我家\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Welcome to my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你知道我最担心的是什么吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You know what bothers me so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:17:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不知道 这个破镇子又迎来美好的一天\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No. It's just another lovely day in shit town.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.96,0:17:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,‎有三件事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Three things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,‎很好 慢慢说来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, good. A list.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,‎第一 你还是个差劲的人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}One: You're still a terrible human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我从来没说要做别人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Never claimed to be anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那也没什么好处\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That doesn't make it better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,‎第二 你说得对\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Two: You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我可能要昏过去了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I may faint dead away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.46,0:17:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,‎闭嘴\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们总是被动应对 ‎一件事接着一件事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We've been running from event to event,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.54,0:17:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,‎而不是站稳脚跟 主动出击\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}reacting instead of planting our feet and just acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但我也被卷入了这场冒险\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But I've also been caught up in the adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.66,0:17:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这让我忘了一些事情\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And it's making me forget things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,‎比如\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Such as?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.33,0:17:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,‎第三\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Third:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这个烂摊子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们在做力所能及的事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, they're doing what they can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.30,0:17:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不 他们没有思考\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No, they're not thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们都吓坏了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They're in shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 我知道\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但还是个烂摊子 你看\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But it's still a mess. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我的族人在世界各地组成了社区\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I come from a people who have weaved a community across the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.21,0:17:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我知道你了解那个社区是做什么的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and I know you know what that community does.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.75,0:17:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,‎能解决问题\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It fixes things,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.37,0:18:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,还能记住过去\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and it remembers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我在这里见到的人都忘了过去\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}All I see here are people who've forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,‎等等\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.04,0:18:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是的 你们这些人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes, you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.54,0:18:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不要用那种眼神看我\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No, don't look at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,‎听着 你不能把厕所建在你睡觉和做饭的地方旁边\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Listen, you cannot put latrines that close to where you sleep and cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.37,0:18:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你们都会生病的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You'll all get sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.33,0:18:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这不是难事 你们把食物存放在哪里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This isn't hard. Where are you storing your food?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,‎宫廷需要这个\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The court needs this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,‎以上帝的名义 ‎你要向统治者献上贡品\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You will by God give tribute to your rulers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这可不行\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, hell, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,‎什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.91,0:18:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你想让人们交出他们能找到的一点食物\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You want these people to give up what little food they can find
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,‎给你不露面的国王和王后吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to your invisible king and queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这里对他们来说不安全\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's not safe for them up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这些人不吃饭对他们也不安全\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And it's not safe for these people to give up eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,‎别碍我的事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Don't get in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我知道我们站在同一边\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I realize that we are on the same side,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但你要知道 我用眼神就能杀了你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}but you need to understand that I can kill you by looking at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我也注意到 这些人需要组织\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I also realize that these people need to organize.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们需要…\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They need...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.97,0:18:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎除非他们自救 否则他们帮不了你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They can't help you until they help themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.35,0:19:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你不露面的国王和王后只能去统治死人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Otherwise, your invisible king and queen will rule over nothing but bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你觉得他们想要这样吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Do you think that's what they want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,‎-嗯...  ‎-你觉得呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}- Well... - Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.56,0:19:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那你可以帮我\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So you can give me a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.85,0:19:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这些车是你的吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Are these carts yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.68,0:19:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不是吗 那些是他的吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No? Those are his?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.26,0:19:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们得把东西拉过来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We need to pull them around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.18,0:19:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们后面的这些建筑清理干净了吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Have these buildings behind us been cleared?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.56,0:19:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,‎建筑废弃了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They're abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你不止这点聪明\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You are cleverer than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这个城市到处都是黑暗生物\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This city is overrun with night creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们来自某个地方\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They're coming from somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,‎第一条原则是保证你的住所安全\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}First rule is make your shelter safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你能找些卫兵帮这些人清理建筑吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Can some of your fellow fighters help these people clear these buildings?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,‎如果有地下宫廷的话\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}If there's an underground court,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,‎城市下面肯定有一连串的洞穴\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}then there's got to be a series of catacombs under the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,‎像格雷捷特一样\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Like Gresit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.06,0:19:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,‎因为如果地下只有一个藏身地\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Because if there was just one underground location,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.43,0:19:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,‎早就被吸血鬼发现了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}it would have been found by the vampires already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:20:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们肯定躲在庞大的地道和洞穴网络里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They have to have been hiding inside an extensive network of tunnels and spaces.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,‎规模庞大到足以让该死的吸血鬼也在下面筑巢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Extensive enough that the bloody vampires are nesting down there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.51,0:20:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这些家伙无处不在\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And these things must be everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我开始这段旅程时 我的计划很简单\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}When I began this journey, I had a very simple plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那个计划已经变了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That plan has evolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.85,0:21:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,‎现在的计划是征服\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The plan is now conquest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.47,0:21:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你们要杀光所有人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Kill everything you see!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.01,0:21:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,‎除了锻造师赫克托\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Except Hector the forgemaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.22,0:22:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他只能留给我\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He is for me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.43,0:22:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,‎开始\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Begin!
